---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Contact';
const sent = Astro.url.searchParams.get('sent') === '1';

const FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT = 'https://formspree.io/f/xnjnpgjp';
const NEXT_URL = 'https://3dsl.jp/contact?sent=1';
---

<Layout title={title} description="Contact the 3DSL site owner.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Contact</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-white/70">
      ご意見・不具合報告・掲載依頼などは、下のフォームからお送りください。
    </p>

    {sent && (
      <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-500/30 bg-emerald-500/10 p-4 text-emerald-200">
        送信ありがとうございます。
      </div>
    )}

    <form
      class="mt-8 space-y-4"
      action={FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT}
      method="POST"
    >
      <input type="hidden" name="_next" value={NEXT_URL} />

      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm text-white/70" for="email">Email</label>
        <input
          id="email"
          name="email"
          type="email"
          required
          class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-4 py-2 text-white placeholder-white/30 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/20"
          placeholder="you@example.com"
        />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm text-white/70" for="subject">Subject</label>
        <input
          id="subject"
          name="subject"
          type="text"
          class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-4 py-2 text-white placeholder-white/30 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/20"
          placeholder="(optional)"
        />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm text-white/70" for="message">Message</label>
        <textarea
          id="message"
          name="message"
          required
          rows={8}
          class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-4 py-2 text-white placeholder-white/30 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/20"
          placeholder="What's on your mind?"
        ></textarea>
      </div>

      <button
        type="submit"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white text-neutral-900 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-white/90"
      >
        Send
      </button>
    </form>

    <p class="mt-8 text-xs text-white/50">
      送信内容は対応のためにのみ利用します。返信が必要な場合は、メールアドレスをご入力ください。
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
